138
00:11:44,082 --> 00:11:45,292
Kita, Suku Bato dan Ago,

139
00:11:45,375 --> 00:11:48,628
sudah lama tidak berinteraksi
karena dipisahkan Sungai Notsan.

140
00:11:48,712 --> 00:11:51,923
